{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-30-digit-n-powers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 30: Broj n za stepene cifra","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Iznenadno, postoji samo tri broja koja mogu biti napisana kao zbir četvrtih stepeni njihovih cifara:</p>\n<div style='margin-left: 4em;'>\n  1634 = 1<sup>4</sup> + 6<sup>4</sup> + 3<sup>4</sup> + 4<sup>4</sup><br>\n  8208 = 8<sup>4</sup> + 2<sup>4</sup> + 0<sup>4</sup> + 8<sup>4</sup><br>\n  9474 = 9<sup>4</sup> + 4<sup>4</sup> + 7<sup>4</sup> + 4<sup>4</sup><br>\n</div>\n<p>Pošto je 1 = 1<sup>4</sup> nije ukupan iznos, pa nije uključen.</p>\n<p>Zbir ovih brojeva je 1634 + 8208 + 9474 = 19316.</p>\n<p>Pronađite zbir svih brojeva koji se mogu zapisati kao <code>n</code> stepeni njihovih cifara.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f38a1000cf542c50fe9d","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301953,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-30-digit-n-powers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function digitnPowers(n) {\n\n  return n;\n}\n\ndigitnPowers(5);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>digitnPowers(2)</code> Trebalo bi vratiti broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof digitnPowers(2) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>digitnPowers(2)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 0.</p>","testString":"assert(digitnPowers(2) == 0);"},{"text":"<p><code>digitnPowers(3)</code> treba da vrati 1301.</p>","testString":"assert(digitnPowers(3) == 1301);"},{"text":"<p><code>digitnPowers(4)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 19316.</p>","testString":"assert(digitnPowers(4) == 19316);"},{"text":"<p><code>digitnPowers(5)</code> treba da vrati 443839.</p>","testString":"assert(digitnPowers(5) == 443839);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-30-digit-n-powers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-31-coin-sums","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-29-distinct-powers","id":"5900f38a1000cf542c50fe9d","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-30-digit-n-powers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}